      <title>亿万富翁阿里的轰动性 IPO 吸引了阿联酋印度裔大亨的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/billionaire-yusuff-ali-s-lulu-ipo-spotlights-uae-s-india-born-tycoons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1973 年，十几岁的尤素夫·阿里来到阿联酋，当时这个国家只有 50 万人口。第二年，他在首都阿布扎比开设了第一家杂货店，随后借助多年的石油繁荣，他开始了疯狂的扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/billionaire-yusuff-ali-s-lulu-ipo-spotlights-uae-s-india-born-tycoons</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选后，伊隆·马斯克的净资产突破 3000 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/elon-musk-s-net-worth-tops-300-billion-in-wake-of-trump-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们押注埃隆·马斯克与当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的密切关系将提振特斯拉公司的发展，该公司股价飙升，埃隆·马斯克的净资产近三年来首次超过 3000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/elon-musk-s-net-worth-tops-300-billion-in-wake-of-trump-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 21:47:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AppLovin 首席执行官曾被风险投资公司拒绝，如今身价 110 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/applovin-ceo-adam-foroughi-s-net-worth-reaches-10-billion-on-stock-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十多年前，当 AppLovin Corp. 联合创始人 Adam Foroughi 向湾区风险投资公司推销其刚刚起步的广告技术业务时，他遭到了所有风险投资公司的拒绝。但他笑到了最后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/applovin-ceo-adam-foroughi-s-net-worth-reaches-10-billion-on-stock-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 19:27:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rizk 退出导致 40 亿美元资金流出，Fiera 股价下跌 11%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/star-manager-s-departure-costs-fiera-capital-another-4-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大资产管理公司 Fiera Capital Corp. 因另一位基金经理终止与该公司的咨询协议而损失了 55 亿加元（40 亿美元）的委托。该公司股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/star-manager-s-departure-costs-fiera-capital-another-4-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:48:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
